===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm}}, from {{der|en|fro|ablatif||the ablative case}}, from {{der|en|la|ablātīvus||expressing removal}},<ref>{{R:American Heritage Dictionary|edition=1971|page=3}}</ref> from {{m|la|ablātus||taken away}}, from {{m|la|auferō||I take away}}. The engineering/nautical sense originates from {{m|en|ablate}} + {{m|en|-ive}}.

